AddressInfo.Title: AAA Bob Sumerel Tire & Service Maineville

GeneralComments: We are excited to announce that we have installed a new GoSpace EVM7700 Dual Charging Station with our new Open Charge system, EVSuite. AAA is still offering FREE charging. Just follow the instructions on the large 8-inch monitor.  Swipe any credit card to activate the EV Charger. While you are there, feel free to stop into the AAA Branch for all your traveling and membership needs. If you have any questions, feel free to contact the GoSpace Support team at 813.421.5121
